data.description: Welcome to this inviting split foyer home nestled in the sought-after Northeast area of Beatrice. Featuring three bedrooms, it offers a generous layout complemented by a spacious fenced backyard. Within the past four years, significant upgrades have been made, including a new roof, gas water heater, bathroom vanity faucet, tub/shower faucet, and new LVP flooring. The kitchen has been tastefully renovated with fresh countertops and cabinets, enhancing the overall appeal. Step outside to discover a charming patio nestled beneath a picturesque deck, perfect for hosting outdoor gatherings. Rounding out this property is an additional parking pad adjacent to the driveway, providing convenient space for extra items.
